    <comment>New package: grok-build - xAI's terminal AI coding agent (grok CLI/TUI). Rust, Apache-2.0, /usr/bin/grok. Self-updater and telemetry disabled; offline build; build-memory constrained to avoid OOM on low-RAM aarch64 workers. Devel: devel:tools.</comment>
